name: PRE-ORDER: FULL BLOOM TEE LIGHT BLUE
description:
STAYBUGGIN.COM

Our third t-shirt installment since we've been up and running. The Full Bloom Tee is printed on quality Gildan Ultra Cotton T-shirts. The shirt features our Bug Life logo in a 3D floral image. We hope you like it!

Size's are available from S-XL. Make sure you verify the size you want in your checkout information, seeing that a drop down menu is not available upon checkout. You will need to write a message during checkout or on the PayPal slip. If we do not hear from you, we will try our best to get in touch through email.

Shirts are extremely limited. First come, first serve.

You can expect delivery between 3-4 weeks upon checkout.

Thanks for the support!
